quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,( ae paighambar un munhkiran islam se ) keh do ke ae kafroo !
  109,2,jin ( buton ) ko tum poochtay ho un ko mein nahi poojta
  109,3,aur jis ( khuda ) ki mein ibadat karta hon is ki tum ibadat nahi karte
  109,4,aur ( mein phir kehta hon ke ) jin ki tum parastish karte hon un ki mein parastish karne wala nahi hon
  109,5,aur nah tum is ki bandagi karne walay ( maloom hotay ) ho jis ki mein bandagi karta hon
  109,6,tum apne deen par mein apne deen par
  110,1,jab khuda ki madad aa pohanchi aur fatah ( haasil ho gayi )
  110,2,aur tum ne dekh liya ke log ghool ke ghool khuda ke deen mein daakhil ho rahay hain
  110,3,"to apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karo aur is se mughfirat mango, be shak woh maaf karne wala hai"
  111,1,abu lahab ke haath tooten aur woh halaak ho
  111,2,nah to is ka maal hi is ke kuch kaam aaya aur nah woh jo is ne kamaya
  111,3,woh jald bharakti hui aag mein daakhil ho ga
  111,4,aur is ki joru bhi jo eendhan sir par uthaye phurti hai
  111,5,is ke gilaay mein monj ki rssi ho gi
